Revision history for Data-MinHash-Shared

0.02      2026-07-12
          - Add b-bit MinHash: bbit_similarity (Jaccard from the low b bits with
            the 2^-b collision correction), bbit_signature (compact packed
            snapshot), and the static bbit_similarity_of to compare snapshots.

0.01      2026-07-10
          - Initial release.
